      • setScheduleID

        public void setScheduleID(java.lang.Integer scheduleID)
        Added to bridge the inconsistency in bullhorn form between add and edit note. Add note uses scheduleID and edit note uses userCommentID to refer to the id. This setter method will be used by Spring to map the scheduleID request param to the userCommentID field
        Parameters:
        scheduleID -
